{
"#name"
:
{
"eget"
:
null
,
"en"
:
"Download and install binaries from GitHub/GitLab/Codeberg Releases"
,
"cn"
:
"从 GitHub/GitLab/Codeberg Release 下载并安装二进制文件"
}
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Download and install pre-built binaries from GitHub/GitLab/Codeberg Releases (Inspired by zyedidia/eget)"
,
"cn"
:
"从 GitHub/GitLab/Codeberg Release 下载并安装预编译二进制文件（Inspired by zyedidia/eget）"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"纯 shell 重新实现，100% 兼容 zyedidia/eget CLI（inactive）。MIT License。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Pure shell reimplementation, 100% compatible with zyedidia/eget CLI (inactive). MIT License.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"推荐用法：x eget --to ~/.local/bin user/repo。x-cmd 会自动将 ~/.local/bin 加入 PATH。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Recommended: x eget --to ~/.local/bin user/repo. x-cmd automatically adds ~/.local/bin to PATH.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"多平台支持：GitHub、GitLab、Codeberg。短名 gh:/gl:/cb: 快速指定平台。\n例如 x eget gl:owner/repo 从 GitLab 下载。暂不支持 Gitee（Release 下载需登录）。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Multi-forge support: GitHub, GitLab, Codeberg. Use short names gh:/gl:/cb: to specify.\ne.g., x eget gl:owner/repo downloads from GitLab. Gitee not supported (requires login).\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"x eget 直接从作者仓库下载，可按需获取所有版本。x pkg 是 x-cmd 官方打包维护的稳定发行渠道，只引入经过验证的稳定版本。\n"
,
"en"
:
"x eget downloads directly from the author's repo — all versions available on demand. x pkg is x-cmd's curated stable channel, only shipping vetted releases.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"开发者按规范打包并发布到 Release，用户通过 x eget 即下即用，通过 x eget snap 即下即运行。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Developers package and publish to releases following naming conventions, users download instantly with x eget and run instantly with x eget snap.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"自动 SHA-256 校验：下载后利用 GitHub Release API 的 digest 字段验证文件完整性。即使用户通过 GHPROXY 下载，校验数据仍来自 GitHub API，防止中间篡改。可通过 --no-verify 跳过。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Auto SHA-256 verification: after download, verifies file integrity using GitHub Release API digest. Even with GHPROXY, verification data comes from GitHub API directly, preventing tampering. Skip with --no-verify.\n"
}
]
,
"#tip:note"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"环境变量 `___X_CMD_GHPROXY_ENDPOINT`：GitHub 直连慢时走代理。仅作用于 github.com 资源下载，不影响 api.github.com 与其它 forge（gitlab / codeberg）。\n支持两种写法，自动识别：\n  - 前缀型：`___X_CMD_GHPROXY_ENDPOINT=\"https://your-proxy.example.com\"`         => https://your-proxy.example.com/https://github.com/...\n  - 替换型：`___X_CMD_GHPROXY_ENDPOINT=\"https://your-proxy.example.com/github.com\"` => https://your-proxy.example.com/github.com/...\n末尾斜杠两种模式都会自动去掉。设置后 `x eget` / `x eget snap` 的下载链路均生效；下载日志会打印 `Using GHPROXY: ...` 提示。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Env `___X_CMD_GHPROXY_ENDPOINT`: route slow GitHub downloads through a proxy. Applies only to github.com asset downloads — api.github.com and other forges (gitlab / codeberg) are unaffected.\nTwo endpoint shapes are auto-detected:\n  - prefix:  `___X_CMD_GHPROXY_ENDPOINT=\"https://your-proxy.example.com\"`         => https://your-proxy.example.com/https://github.com/...\n  - replace: `___X_CMD_GHPROXY_ENDPOINT=\"https://your-proxy.example.com/github.com\"` => https://your-proxy.example.com/github.com/...\nTrailing slashes are normalized. Once set, both `x eget` and `x eget snap` are affected; download log prints `Using GHPROXY: ...`.\n"
}
]
,
