"x eget snap [OPTIONS] <repo> [-- args...]"
:
null
}
]
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"首次下载后缓存到本地，后续调用零网络开销。\n"
,
"en"
:
"First run downloads and caches locally; subsequent runs have zero network overhead.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"--auto-check-update 1d：超过 1 天自动检查 GitHub Release 是否有新版本。间隔最小 5m；检查失败后同样至少等 5 分钟再重试。\n"
,
"en"
:
"--auto-check-update 1d: auto-check GitHub Release for new versions after 1 day. Minimum interval 5m; on failure, same 5m cooldown before retry.\n"
}
]
,
